OL,6,FHowever, he made no mention of going
OL,7,Fagainst protocol and keeping the
OL,8,Fdeclaration secret from partner
OL,9,Fservices when interviewed in 2018 as
OL,10,Fpart of the Kerslake Report, an
OL,11,Findependent review into the emergency
OL,12,Fresponse commissioned by Greater
