OL,6,FHowever, the review found there was
OL,7,Fsufficient evidence for a disciplinary
OL,8,Fhearing to take place, which will be
OL,9,Forganised by Greater Manchester Police.
OL,11,FIOPC regional director Emily Barry
OL,12,Fsaid: "This was a highly complex and
OL,13,Fchallenging investigation. In
OL,14,Fcircumstances like these, thorough
OL,15,Fscrutiny ` both of the police, and our
OL,16,Fown decision-making, through our
OL,17,FVictims' Right to Review process ` is
OL,18,Fessential to allow the public to have
OL,19,Fconfidence in the police complaints
OL,20,Fprocess.
